《'''手持圓形聖像的年輕男子'''》（[[意大利语|意大利语]]：Giovane uomo con in mano una medaglia）是[[桑德罗·波提切利|桑德罗·波提切利]]的畫作。依據作品的風格來推斷，作畫時間大約是在1480年前後<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|last=Thomas|first=Gina|title=Mehr als 80 Millionen Dollar: Dieser Jüngling kann teuer werden|language=de|work=FAZ.NET|url=https://www.faz.net/1.6971296|access-date=2020-09-27|issn=0174-4909|archive-date=2021-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210815131126/https://www.faz.net/aktuell/feuilleton/kunstmarkt/mehr-als-80-millionen-dollar-dieser-juengling-kann-teuer-werden-16971296.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。畫中人物的身份不明，但分析家認為可能是[[美第奇家族|美第奇家族]]成員<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|date=2020-09-24|title='True beauty for the ages': $80m Botticelli to appear at auction|url=http://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2020/sep/24/true-beauty-for-the-ages-80m-botticelli-to-appear-at-auction|access-date=2020-09-27|website=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129172429/https://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2020/sep/24/true-beauty-for-the-ages-80m-botticelli-to-appear-at-auction|dead-url=no}}</ref>，因為[[洛伦佐·德·美第奇|洛伦佐·德·美第奇]]是波提切利的主要贊助者之一<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|date=2020-09-24|title='True beauty for the ages': $80m Botticelli to appear at auction|url=http://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2020/sep/24/true-beauty-for-the-ages-80m-botticelli-to-appear-at-auction|access-date=2020-09-27|website=the Guardian|language=en}}</ref>。該作品代表了[[文藝復興時期|文藝復興時期]][[佛罗伦萨|佛罗伦萨]]上流社會的審美觀念<ref>{{Cite web|last=McGreevy|first=Nora|title=One of the Last Privately Owned Botticelli Portraits Could Fetch $80 Million|url=https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/rare-botticelli-portrait-could-sell-over-80-million-180975908/|access-date=2020-12-19|website=Smithsonian Magazine|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208000446/https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/rare-botticelli-portrait-could-sell-over-80-million-180975908/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-09-25|title=Rare Botticelli portrait could reach $100 million at auction|language=en|work=Reuters|url=https://uk.reuters.com/article/us-art-auction-botticelli-idUSKCN26F1MZ|access-date=2020-12-19|archive-date=2021-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210830140208/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-art-auction-botticelli-idUSKCN26F1MZ?edition-redirect=uk|dead-url=no}}</ref>。畫中人物穿著的服飾是一件質地優良的藍色[[丘尼卡|丘尼卡]]，它的色彩在當時非常罕見<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sandro Botticelli: A Closer Look at Young Man Holding a Roundel|url=https://www.mutualart.com/Article/Botticelli--A-Closer-Look-at-Young-Man-H/C437B92C2B1FD2A8|access-date=2020-12-19|website=www.mutualart.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110081648/https://www.mutualart.com/Article/Botticelli--A-Closer-Look-at-Young-Man-H/C437B92C2B1FD2A8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這是一幅[[蛋彩畫|蛋彩畫]]作品，長度為58.7厘米，寬度為38.9厘米。圓盤中的聖人圖案是在肖像完成之後添加上去的。

這幅作品曾經在[[大都會藝術博物館|大都會藝術博物館]]、[[國家美術館_(倫敦)|國家美術館]]以及[[施泰德藝術館|施泰德藝術館]]展出<ref name=":1" />。

2021年1月，該畫作在紐約[[蘇富比|蘇富比]]拍賣會上以超过9220萬美元的價格被出售<ref>{{Cite web|title=Botticelli portrait sells for record $92.1m at Sotheby's in New York|url=http://www.theartnewspaper.com/news/botticelli-portrait-sells-for-at-sotheby-s-in-new-york|access-date=2021-01-28|website=www.theartnewspaper.com|archive-date=2021-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317113551/https://www.theartnewspaper.com/news/botticelli-portrait-sells-for-at-sotheby-s-in-new-york|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

